text.data-name: The recent event of demonetization gave rise to a lot of issues

svg.text: The recent event of demonetization gave rise to a lot of issues and concerns for an average Indian citizen . One of such concerns was the vivid design and colors of the new notes. Where the popularity of thesenotes is debatable the jolting color scheme isnt. The following visualization represents the drastic shift in the circulation of varied different colored notes over the years.
